1800:Ayase slowly turned toward her, and then took the thermometer out from under her arm like she'd just remembered it was there.[%p]
1900:The nurse looked at the number on the digital display and wrote it down on the chart.[%p]
2000:[name]看護師[line]37.1 degrees Celsius.[%p]
