2600:The nurse spoke with a smile and took the thermometer. Her expression was gentle, and there was something about her that put a patient at ease.[%p]
2700:But Ayase put her hand to her forehead and shook her head.[%p]
2800:Ever since she came here, Ayase had been dealing with a dull headache. “Painful” wasn't the word for it.[%p]
2900:But there was an unpleasant sensation of something pulsing in her head. It was making it hard for her to think.[%p]
3000:And her whole body felt as heavy as lead.[%p]
3100:This had happened to Ayase before, too. It was when she was at Ark Heart Medical.[%p]
3200:The headaches had lasted 24 hours a day, 365 days a year. She'd been unable to sleep, and emotionally unstable.[%p]
3300:It was a past she didn't want to remember. A past she'd sealed away. Her memories of two years ago...[%p]
3400:The pain was the trigger that made them come flashing back.[%p]
3500:A dark room. A small window with bars.[%p]
3600:Except for the small window, the walls were entirely covered with mirrors. She'd been restrained in a steel chair in the center of the room.[%p]
3700:There was some kind of device on her head, with cords stretching off of it.[%p]
3800:Her hands were bound behind the chair's back.[%p]
3900:Her head was restrained at a slight angle.[%p]
4000:There was no one else in the room.[%p]
4100:The only sounds were her panting for air, and the straining of the metal chair.[%p]
4200:[name]あやせ[line]Aaah! Aaaah![%p]
4300:Drool was flying from her lips, and a bestial howl was coming from her throat that one would've thought impossible for a girl her age.[%p]
4400:[name]あやせ[line]Kill me![%p]
4500:[name]あやせ[line]KILL ME![%p]
4600:It was a very quiet form of torture.[%p]
4700:There was only one thing they were doing to her.[%p]
4800:A single drop of water was falling on her forehead from above, in the same spot every time, at precise five-second intervals.[%p]
4900:That was all.[%p]
5000:She'd been stuck like that for two days with no rest.[%p]
5100:And now all she could think of was when the next drop would fall.[%p]
5200:Her senses were pushed to their limits.[%p]
5300:Each time a drop fell,[%p]
5400:it felt like all the nerves in her body were being ripped apart.[%p]
5500:Like all the bones in her body were being shattered to pieces.[%p]
5600:Like a long sharp awl was being driven into her skull.[%p]
5700:Like all the fluids in her body, including her blood, were freezing.[%p]
5800:Like all her skin was rotting and sloughing off.[%p]
5900:It was more than enough to drive her mad.[%p]
6000:[name]あやせ[line]Hahh... Hahh...[%p]
